    Scope and Contents
FIRST CONGREGATIONAL CHURCH 
Robert Lewis, member of Springfield's First Congregational Church, recalls becoming a member; the 1956 church fire, fundraising, rebuilding, and the groundbreaking ceremonies; the  role of women; choir; affiliation with United Church of Christ; and the strengths and weaknesses of the church. 1 tape, 90 mins., 18 pp. 
Interview by Henry Russel, 1980 
